WEBVTT

00:00:44.362 --> 00:00:49.137
=The Hidden Heir Ye Chen=
(Adapted from "The Peerless Son-in-Law")

00:00:49.650 --> 00:00:52.225
=Episode 24=

00:00:52.925 --> 00:00:54.079
(Longting One)
A little thank-you.

00:00:54.359 --> 00:00:54.960
Please accept it.

00:00:55.562 --> 00:00:56.712
(Longting One)
Longting One?

00:00:56.880 --> 00:00:57.159
Yes.

00:00:57.500 --> 00:00:58.960
The most expensive estate in Jinzhou.

00:00:59.640 --> 00:01:00.479
A05,

00:01:00.479 --> 00:01:02.719
the largest villa there.

00:01:04.479 --> 00:01:05.280
I'm sorry,

00:01:05.737 --> 00:01:06.786
but this isn't what I want.

00:01:09.325 --> 00:01:11.319
I know exactly what you want,

00:01:11.680 --> 00:01:13.319
but I can't grant that.

00:01:14.040 --> 00:01:16.040
I have to honor my late friend's wish.

00:01:16.439 --> 00:01:17.599
Aside from the formula,

00:01:17.840 --> 00:01:18.959
anything else,

00:01:19.200 --> 00:01:21.040
I'd give with both hands.

00:01:21.799 --> 00:01:23.359
Even Ye Changying and An Chengqi's

00:01:23.359 --> 00:01:24.120
son?

00:01:24.920 --> 00:01:26.159
Yes, only to him.

00:01:26.880 --> 00:01:28.359
That child belonged to my old friend.

00:01:28.359 --> 00:01:29.680
It was his to begin with.

00:01:31.079 --> 00:01:32.079
Unfortunately,

00:01:32.319 --> 00:01:34.280
he's no longer alive.

00:01:38.079 --> 00:01:39.200
How do you know?

00:01:39.519 --> 00:01:40.359
Mr. Qin,

00:01:41.519 --> 00:01:42.439
I'm not dead.

00:01:47.719 --> 00:01:48.920
I'm

00:01:49.439 --> 00:01:50.879
Ye Chen,

00:01:51.640 --> 00:01:52.439
their son.

00:02:02.680 --> 00:02:03.480
You look

00:02:05.799 --> 00:02:06.599
just like them.

00:02:07.560 --> 00:02:08.319
The eyes,

00:02:09.120 --> 00:02:09.879
the nose,

00:02:10.439 --> 00:02:11.239
the face.

00:02:11.400 --> 00:02:12.560
So much like your parents.

00:02:13.359 --> 00:02:14.159
Ye Chen,

00:02:14.800 --> 00:02:16.000
you're really alive?

00:02:19.039 --> 00:02:20.400
This is amazing!

00:02:24.439 --> 00:02:25.560
I must have been blind.

00:02:26.225 --> 00:02:27.785
How did I not see it sooner?

00:02:30.360 --> 00:02:30.879
Wait here.

00:02:43.560 --> 00:02:44.159
Ye Chen,

00:02:44.159 --> 00:02:44.680
take this.

00:02:49.159 --> 00:02:52.319
Years ago, when your dad
planned to return with the formula,

00:02:52.520 --> 00:02:53.759
he secretly gave me

00:02:54.280 --> 00:02:56.680
this USB drive
containing part of the data.

00:02:57.900 --> 00:02:59.130
That car accident back then

00:02:59.775 --> 00:03:00.940
wasn't an accident.

00:03:02.240 --> 00:03:03.199
You mean someone

00:03:03.960 --> 00:03:05.159
tried to steal the formula

00:03:05.510 --> 00:03:07.599
and caused the car accident
that killed my parents?

00:03:08.080 --> 00:03:08.639
Including

00:03:09.000 --> 00:03:10.560
your appearance and Madam Li's death,

00:03:10.919 --> 00:03:13.120
maybe all of that was part of the plan.

00:03:13.800 --> 00:03:14.680
So do you

00:03:15.439 --> 00:03:17.639
still think all of this was

00:03:18.800 --> 00:03:20.120
just a coincidence?

00:03:25.919 --> 00:03:27.319
After the tragedy

00:03:27.675 --> 00:03:29.623
in the Ye family,

00:03:30.439 --> 00:03:31.280
they tried

00:03:31.537 --> 00:03:33.199
to find you but got no leads.

00:03:33.400 --> 00:03:34.560
Later,

00:03:34.560 --> 00:03:35.120
they even

00:03:35.759 --> 00:03:36.759
said you were dead.

00:03:38.680 --> 00:03:40.240
That's not what Tang Sihai told me.

00:03:40.560 --> 00:03:41.719
Looks like

00:03:42.162 --> 00:03:43.755
he hid you on purpose.

00:03:44.439 --> 00:03:45.462
He was

00:03:45.512 --> 00:03:47.475
your dad's personal butler.

00:03:47.537 --> 00:03:49.639
But a year before the accident,

00:03:49.937 --> 00:03:51.362
they had a huge fight

00:03:51.412 --> 00:03:53.400
and never spoke again.

00:03:54.325 --> 00:03:55.973
Do you suspect him?

00:03:56.812 --> 00:03:58.879
I suspect everyone.

00:04:08.137 --> 00:04:09.475
I've tried so hard

00:04:09.475 --> 00:04:11.039
to remember my parents,

00:04:13.280 --> 00:04:14.280
but nothing comes back.

00:04:16.175 --> 00:04:18.599
Even their faces
are fading from my memory.

00:04:20.360 --> 00:04:21.439
It's normal.

00:04:22.560 --> 00:04:24.325
You were so young,

00:04:24.530 --> 00:04:25.920
and you went through so much trauma.

00:04:26.720 --> 00:04:27.720
They wouldn't blame you.

00:04:31.480 --> 00:04:32.759
Their deaths weren't accidents.

00:04:33.487 --> 00:04:34.720
Like Madam Li,

00:04:35.720 --> 00:04:37.200
they died because of me.

00:04:38.319 --> 00:04:39.120
Ye Chen,

00:04:39.959 --> 00:04:40.800
don't blame yourself.

00:04:41.275 --> 00:04:42.638
If it weren't for my illness,

00:04:43.230 --> 00:04:44.951
they wouldn't have
researched the formula.

00:04:45.759 --> 00:04:47.279
If it weren't for the formula, I...

00:04:47.279 --> 00:04:49.319
The world doesn't work on "ifs."

00:04:49.839 --> 00:04:51.160
You did nothing wrong.

00:04:51.800 --> 00:04:52.519
Blame those

00:04:52.720 --> 00:04:54.600
who tried to steal the formula.

00:04:58.839 --> 00:04:59.920
I'll find them.

00:05:01.240 --> 00:05:02.480
All of them.

00:05:04.639 --> 00:05:05.439
Them?

00:05:07.040 --> 00:05:08.680
Qin Gang gave me his belongings.

00:05:09.350 --> 00:05:10.311
I've checked.

00:05:10.575 --> 00:05:13.079
Only one piece remains
for the complete formula.

00:05:13.920 --> 00:05:15.000
Who do you think

00:05:15.519 --> 00:05:16.600
has it?

00:05:22.575 --> 00:05:24.287
(Tang Sihai)

00:05:27.720 --> 00:05:28.759
You suspect Tang Sihai?

00:05:28.950 --> 00:05:30.600
If Qin Gang's right,

00:05:30.687 --> 00:05:31.759
he's linked

00:05:32.212 --> 00:05:33.832
to my parents' deaths

00:05:34.300 --> 00:05:36.062
and Madam Li's.

00:05:39.199 --> 00:05:39.879
Churan,

00:05:41.399 --> 00:05:42.525
no matter who he is,

00:05:43.075 --> 00:05:44.715
I won't let them get away.

00:05:46.680 --> 00:05:47.487
I want you

00:05:49.137 --> 00:05:51.360
to take your parents
and hide until I finish...

00:05:51.360 --> 00:05:52.180
What are you saying?

00:05:53.759 --> 00:05:55.000
We agreed

00:05:55.562 --> 00:05:57.600
to face hardships together.

00:05:58.212 --> 00:05:59.839
I'll always be by your side.

00:06:28.680 --> 00:06:29.399
Hello.

00:06:29.399 --> 00:06:31.879
The number you dialed isn't answering.

00:06:31.879 --> 00:06:33.150
Please try again later.

00:06:35.550 --> 00:06:36.120
Mr. Tang,

00:06:36.337 --> 00:06:37.439
what do we do now?

00:06:39.550 --> 00:06:41.399
Things are

00:06:42.519 --> 00:06:44.040
getting lively.

00:06:44.412 --> 00:06:46.360
(Dihao Group)
Everyone is finally showing their hand.

00:06:47.075 --> 00:06:49.279
Ye Chen wants to keep that formula.

00:06:51.319 --> 00:06:53.000
It won't be easy.

00:06:59.800 --> 00:07:12.319
♪Happy birthday to you♪

00:07:12.319 --> 00:07:13.240
Happy birthday.

00:07:14.600 --> 00:07:15.600
Whose birthday?

00:07:18.639 --> 00:07:20.079
Yours.

00:07:20.639 --> 00:07:22.639
I didn't even know my birthday.

00:07:23.639 --> 00:07:24.720
From now on,

00:07:25.160 --> 00:07:26.759
today's your birthday.

00:07:26.760 --> 00:07:27.920
This is not just your birthday.

00:07:27.920 --> 00:07:30.120
It's a fresh start for our whole family.

00:07:31.187 --> 00:07:32.025
Chen,

00:07:33.000 --> 00:07:34.275
I'm sorry.

00:07:35.360 --> 00:07:36.639
It took me over a year

00:07:38.000 --> 00:07:39.560
to see how good you are.

00:07:40.680 --> 00:07:42.120
You're not just good to Churan.

00:07:42.360 --> 00:07:43.199
You've

00:07:43.720 --> 00:07:45.040
been great to us too.

00:07:45.399 --> 00:07:47.160
Thank you

00:07:47.700 --> 00:07:49.120
for getting this family

00:07:49.387 --> 00:07:51.079
back on its feet.

00:07:51.439 --> 00:07:52.240
Chen,

00:07:53.000 --> 00:07:54.600
I always knew you were good.

00:07:54.839 --> 00:07:55.800
From now on,

00:07:56.319 --> 00:07:57.199
this is your home.

00:07:57.600 --> 00:07:59.920
Treat us like your parents.

00:08:00.360 --> 00:08:01.120
Our whole family

00:08:01.600 --> 00:08:02.690
will be happy and together.

00:08:04.800 --> 00:08:05.600
Thank you, Dad.

00:08:08.759 --> 00:08:09.560
Thank you, Mom.

00:08:11.360 --> 00:08:12.639
We're family now.

00:08:12.639 --> 00:08:13.879
No need for formalities.

00:08:14.637 --> 00:08:16.219
Come on, light the candles.

00:08:26.620 --> 00:08:27.480
What did you wish for?

00:08:28.439 --> 00:08:29.680
I wished we could

00:08:30.100 --> 00:08:31.988
move into a big house.

00:08:32.279 --> 00:08:32.959
A huge villa.

00:08:33.600 --> 00:08:34.560
That's

00:08:34.560 --> 00:08:35.240
perfect!

00:08:35.240 --> 00:08:36.199
Let's work hard.

00:08:36.199 --> 00:08:37.959
Chen, I trust you!

00:08:38.240 --> 00:08:39.279
Cheers!

00:08:39.480 --> 00:08:40.399
- Cheers!
- Cheers!

00:08:40.399 --> 00:08:41.919
Happy birthday!

00:08:50.775 --> 00:08:52.840
Why did you tell them
you wanted a new house?

00:08:53.039 --> 00:08:54.375
Isn't it fine here?

00:08:54.559 --> 00:08:55.279
It's

00:08:55.279 --> 00:08:56.080
perfect.

00:08:57.039 --> 00:08:59.080
This is the only place
that feels like home.

00:08:59.759 --> 00:09:01.120
Then why did you say that?

00:09:04.759 --> 00:09:06.279
It's a special time.

00:09:06.725 --> 00:09:07.851
As thanks,

00:09:08.120 --> 00:09:09.462
Qin Gang gave me a villa.

00:09:10.360 --> 00:09:11.600
Security's better there.

00:09:12.080 --> 00:09:15.050
(Longting One)
Mr. Hong can watch over your parents.

00:09:16.159 --> 00:09:17.320
Longting One?

00:09:22.080 --> 00:09:23.200
Take a look at this house.

00:09:25.200 --> 00:09:25.919
Chen,

00:09:26.840 --> 00:09:28.360
you really wished for this?

00:09:28.850 --> 00:09:30.515
Seems impossible.

00:09:30.799 --> 00:09:32.039
This is Jinzhou's

00:09:32.240 --> 00:09:33.720
most exclusive estate.

00:09:33.720 --> 00:09:35.399
Just

00:09:35.799 --> 00:09:37.120
the thought

00:09:37.120 --> 00:09:38.000
touches us.

00:09:38.000 --> 00:09:38.679
But let's

00:09:38.679 --> 00:09:39.399
be realistic.

00:09:39.879 --> 00:09:41.679
Let's find something

00:09:41.919 --> 00:09:42.960
more modest.

00:09:44.320 --> 00:09:45.200
Lan,

00:09:45.720 --> 00:09:47.519
you're looking here too?

00:09:48.320 --> 00:09:49.000
We...

00:09:49.480 --> 00:09:51.200
We're just browsing.

00:09:51.440 --> 00:09:53.039
Your old place could use an upgrade.

00:09:53.639 --> 00:09:54.440
Ye Chen,

00:09:54.720 --> 00:09:56.440
heard you're doing well.

00:09:56.559 --> 00:09:58.039
Show your mother-in-law some respect.

00:09:58.039 --> 00:09:58.879
Ye Chen,

00:09:59.039 --> 00:10:00.120
don't just look.

00:10:00.279 --> 00:10:01.360
Buy one.

00:10:01.399 --> 00:10:02.240
With your resources,

00:10:02.240 --> 00:10:03.400
shouldn't be a problem, right?

00:10:03.519 --> 00:10:04.480
Of course.

00:10:05.000 --> 00:10:06.519
As long as they like it.

00:10:07.556 --> 00:10:08.637
If I were buying,

00:10:08.637 --> 00:10:09.956
I wouldn't pick a high-rise.

00:10:10.159 --> 00:10:11.120
It has to be a villa,

00:10:11.120 --> 00:10:12.159
and the biggest one.

00:10:13.480 --> 00:10:14.240
Come here, miss.

00:10:14.240 --> 00:10:14.720
Hurry.

00:10:14.919 --> 00:10:15.759
Yes, sir.

00:10:15.759 --> 00:10:18.137
Introduce your villas

00:10:18.275 --> 00:10:20.399
to this distinguished client.

00:10:21.000 --> 00:10:22.360
Our villa community features

00:10:22.600 --> 00:10:24.987
a unique basement-level design,

00:10:24.987 --> 00:10:26.388
and it creates a synergy

00:10:26.388 --> 00:10:28.227
where one plus one is greater than two.

00:10:28.279 --> 00:10:29.120
Name the price.

00:10:29.130 --> 00:10:30.120
300,000 per square meter.

00:10:30.519 --> 00:10:31.360
300,000?

00:10:31.900 --> 00:10:32.919
What about that A05 unit?

00:10:33.559 --> 00:10:34.320
Right this way.

00:10:34.862 --> 00:10:37.639
A05 is one of our premium properties

00:10:37.800 --> 00:10:38.787
in Longting One.

00:10:39.000 --> 00:10:39.799
Name the price.

00:10:42.575 --> 00:10:43.759
180 million.

00:10:45.879 --> 00:10:47.600
Mom, Dad, do you like it?

00:10:48.960 --> 00:10:49.879
Love it!

00:10:50.080 --> 00:10:52.559
If I could live here,

00:10:52.799 --> 00:10:54.480
I'd die happy!

00:10:54.759 --> 00:10:55.480
But...

00:10:55.480 --> 00:10:56.559
Then this will be our home.

00:10:59.799 --> 00:11:01.159
Sorry, sir,

00:11:01.360 --> 00:11:02.850
this villa's sold.

00:11:02.912 --> 00:11:03.672
I know.

00:11:03.862 --> 00:11:04.675
I'm the owner.

00:11:06.039 --> 00:11:06.840
Ye Chen,

00:11:07.000 --> 00:11:08.519
wake up.

00:11:08.679 --> 00:11:10.399
Stop daydreaming.

00:11:10.519 --> 00:11:11.879
You just spout nonsense.

00:11:12.000 --> 00:11:13.450
I'm not here to look at houses today.

00:11:13.460 --> 00:11:14.590
I'm here to collect the keys.

00:11:15.320 --> 00:11:16.000
(Longting One)
Here's the key card.

00:11:16.080 --> 00:11:16.720
Please check it.

00:11:16.720 --> 00:11:17.679
Alright, sir.

00:11:19.679 --> 00:11:21.440
Will there be another miracle this time?

00:11:23.837 --> 00:11:26.512
(Welcome home, Ye Chen, A05 owner.)
Welcome home,

00:11:26.512 --> 00:11:27.679
Ye Chen, owner of A05.

00:11:29.039 --> 00:11:29.720
Mr. Ye,

00:11:29.720 --> 00:11:30.720
welcome home.

00:11:30.879 --> 00:11:32.240
Let's go.

00:11:36.759 --> 00:11:37.159
Wow!

00:11:37.159 --> 00:11:38.519
So luxurious!

00:11:40.639 --> 00:11:41.320
Wow!

00:11:41.480 --> 00:11:42.480
Look at all this!

00:11:42.480 --> 00:11:44.320
Handmade!

00:11:50.279 --> 00:11:51.759
Mom, Dad,

00:11:51.759 --> 00:11:52.320
even

00:11:52.320 --> 00:11:53.840
a home theater!

00:11:56.000 --> 00:11:56.840
Seen enough?

00:11:56.840 --> 00:11:58.919
Where did you get this money?

00:12:00.080 --> 00:12:00.960
I know.

00:12:01.660 --> 00:12:03.440
You must have
embezzled from the Xiao family.

00:12:04.200 --> 00:12:04.840
Xiao Churan,

00:12:05.399 --> 00:12:07.120
you're bold!

00:12:07.120 --> 00:12:08.120
You're pretty funny.

00:12:08.412 --> 00:12:09.879
Does Xiao Group

00:12:09.879 --> 00:12:11.537
even have this much?

00:12:14.590 --> 00:12:15.840
Where did this villa come from?

00:12:16.279 --> 00:12:18.480
You must have done something illegal!

00:12:18.480 --> 00:12:18.960
Yes,

00:12:19.200 --> 00:12:19.919
that's it!

00:12:19.919 --> 00:12:20.960
Just confess already!

00:12:21.159 --> 00:12:21.799
I...

00:12:21.799 --> 00:12:22.360
Mr. Ye,

00:12:22.799 --> 00:12:24.039
the paperwork's done.

00:12:24.279 --> 00:12:24.975
Here you go.

00:12:25.919 --> 00:12:26.360
Thanks.

00:12:26.975 --> 00:12:28.288
Mr. Qin specifically

00:12:28.387 --> 00:12:29.347
said the villa

00:12:29.347 --> 00:12:31.287
was designed to his taste.

00:12:31.600 --> 00:12:33.639
If you want changes,

00:12:33.919 --> 00:12:35.000
renovate it.

00:12:35.440 --> 00:12:36.262
Thank him for me.

00:12:36.399 --> 00:12:37.087
Will do.

00:12:37.087 --> 00:12:38.597
- Mr. Qin?
- Mr. Qin?

00:12:39.600 --> 00:12:41.660
- Qin Gang gave this to you?
- Qin Gang gave this to you?

00:12:42.300 --> 00:12:43.550
I never said I bought it myself.

00:12:46.237 --> 00:12:49.117
A grand villa in Longting One!

00:12:49.480 --> 00:12:51.100
I finally live here!

00:12:52.840 --> 00:12:53.440
Chen,

00:12:53.440 --> 00:12:54.799
I really have to thank you!

00:12:54.799 --> 00:12:55.500
It's nothing, Mom.

00:12:57.360 --> 00:12:58.440
Why are you leaving so soon?

00:12:58.520 --> 00:12:59.799
Aren't you looking around more?

00:13:02.000 --> 00:13:02.919
Leaving already?

00:13:03.360 --> 00:13:04.720
If the first floor's this grand,

00:13:04.720 --> 00:13:07.000
the second must be amazing!

00:13:08.000 --> 00:13:10.120
Come by often!

00:13:10.240 --> 00:13:11.600
I've lived half my life,

00:13:12.080 --> 00:13:13.720
only to have my younger brother's family

00:13:13.720 --> 00:13:14.759
look down on me!

00:13:14.960 --> 00:13:16.159
Qin Gang

00:13:16.159 --> 00:13:17.320
must be blind!

00:13:17.320 --> 00:13:18.759
Aodong should've been mine,

00:13:18.759 --> 00:13:20.350
and this villa too!

00:13:21.320 --> 00:13:23.399
My villa!

00:13:24.840 --> 00:13:25.399
Hello.

00:13:25.825 --> 00:13:27.159
You were right.

00:13:27.487 --> 00:13:29.487
Ye Chen really
got the villa from Qin Gang.

00:13:30.480 --> 00:13:31.200
Understood.

00:13:32.039 --> 00:13:33.159
Make arrangements.

00:13:33.159 --> 00:13:34.679
I'll handle it here.

00:13:53.987 --> 00:13:56.475
♪They said I was only meant
to gaze at the light♪

00:13:56.562 --> 00:14:00.315
♪Never knowing I am the flame itself♪

00:14:00.775 --> 00:14:05.712
♪I am fireworks, not a fire cast aside♪

00:14:05.875 --> 00:14:08.162
♪I open my eyes amid the ruins♪

00:14:08.475 --> 00:14:11.155
♪No one shields me
from the wind or the sky♪

00:14:12.225 --> 00:14:14.850
♪Let them mock, let them sneer♪

00:14:15.150 --> 00:14:18.162
♪I sharpen my silence into blades♪

00:14:18.362 --> 00:14:21.412
♪Every cold word, I remember♪

00:14:21.525 --> 00:14:24.487
♪Etching my path of defiance
into my heart♪

00:14:24.755 --> 00:14:27.912
♪Fate did not sign my future for me♪

00:14:28.137 --> 00:14:31.887
♪I carved my own light
with clenched fists♪

00:14:31.887 --> 00:14:34.750
♪I belong to no one♪

00:14:34.812 --> 00:14:38.262
♪I am the ember
that refuses to bow to destiny♪

00:14:38.262 --> 00:14:40.937
♪Even if the world burns me into ash♪

00:14:40.937 --> 00:14:47.275
♪I will rise upon those ashes♪